    "headline": "Mastercard’s BVNK Deal Brings Stablecoins Into Undervalued Payments Giant",
    "summary": "Mastercard is acquiring BVNK, a leading stablecoin payments provider, in a $1.8 billion deal. The move brings BVNK's on chain payment rails and digital asset infrastructure directly into Mastercard's network. BVNK had previously partnered with Visa, so this transaction shifts a key stablecoin player into Mastercard's orbit. For investors tracking NYSE:MA, this deal adds a new layer to a business that already sits at the center of global payments. The shares most recently closed at $494.0,...",
